," 16:13:00.596",[76,1655,1656],{"class":193}," [warning] [server stderr] HexSchool TodoList MCP Server starting...\n",[76,1658,1659,1661,1664],{"class":78,"line":478},[76,1660,1602],{"class":82},[76,1662,1663],{"class":86}," 16:13:00.603",[76,1665,1666],{"class":193}," [info] Discovered 2 tools\n",[12,1668,1669],{},"How do we verify it works? Open GitHub Copilot Chat and switch to AI Agent mode.",[12,1671,1672],{},[15,1673],{"alt":1674,"src":1675},"Agent Mode","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fmcp-github-copilot\u002F20250522103719.png",[12,1677,1678],{},"Now you can start asking the AI things like:",[67,1680,1682],{"className":569,"code":1681,"language":571,"meta":72,"style":72},"I want to register a todolist account — email is example-mcp@gmail.com, password is example123, nickname is example\n",[62,1683,1684],{"__ignoreMap":72},[76,1685,1686],{"class":78,"line":79},[76,1687,1681],{},[12,1689,1690],{},"When called, dialogs will pop up asking you to confirm the tool to use. Since this is our own MCP Server, no need to worry — just hit \"Continue\".",[12,1692,1693],{},[15,1694],{"alt":1695,"src":1696},"Continue","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fmcp-ai-chat\u002F20250523162807.png",[12,1698,1699],{},"You'll see the AI's response.",[12,1701,1702],{},[15,1703],{"alt":1704,"src":1705},"Registration successful","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fmcp-ai-chat\u002F20250523162908.png",[12,1707,1708],{},"At this point, we've successfully built a basic MCP Server that can interact with GitHub Copilot Chat. Starting from a register API, we built actual executable tool logic.",[12,1710,1711],{},"Now you can try adding more features — login, add tasks, delete tasks — turning this Server into a real assistant for your AI development.",[12,1713,1714],{},"For reference, here's the complete code on GitHub:",[35,1716,1717],{},[38,1718,1719],{},[51,1720,1723],{"href":1721,"rel":1722},"h